quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  11,63,"O maaki: "eeheymon yim…ďe! Kaalanee kam, si mi laatike e …ďanngannduyee immorde ka Joomi am, O okkii kam immorde ka makko yurmeende, ko hommbo faabotoo mi ka Alla si mi yeddii mo? On …ďeydataa kam si wonaa hayrugol.perte"
  11,64,"Eeheymon yim…ďe am, baa …óoo ko ngelooba wonan¬īde on maande. Tertee mba, mba √Īaama e leydi Alla. Wata on memir-mba bone, lepte …ďa…ótii…óe ke…ďa on"."
  11,65,"∆Āe mborii-ba. o maaki: "ndakmitee ka galleeji mon bal…óe tati! ∆äuum ko fodoore nde fennetaake"."
  11,66,"Nde yamiroore Alla nden arunoo, min da…óndiri Saalihu e …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe won¬īdu…ďe e makko, yur-meende immorde ka amen- e koyeera nden √Īande Pellet Joomi maa, ko KaŇčko woni cemmbin…óo, poolu…óo."
  11,67,"Haacaango ngoon nanngi too√Īu…ďe …ďeen.∆Āe wa…ótini ka galleeji ma…ď…ďe jiccii…ďe.(jus…ďe)."
  11,68,"A sikkay …ďe √Īii…ďaano …óoon. Nganndee pellet Samuudu en njedduno Joomi ma…ď…ďe, nganndee go…ó…óal yurmee- nde (Alla) woodanii Samuuda'en!"
  11,69,"GooŇč…óii Nulaa…ďe amen …ďeen nggaddanii Ibraahiima welo-welo, …ďe mbi'i: "Kisal (e mon)". O maaki: "Kisal (e mon). Nee…ďaani o ardi e ngaari ju…óaandi."
  11,70,"Nde o yi'noo juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óeen njottaaki ndi, o fayti…ďe (o sikkitii), o soomi kulol e ma…ď…ďe. ∆Āe mbi'i: "Wota a hul, ko min nulaa…ďe e yim…ďe Luuti …ďeen"."
  11,71,"Tawi cuddii…óo makko on no darii, o jali, min mbeltiniri mo Ishaaqa, e …ďaawo Ishaaqa, Yaaquube."